<br>
I currently have a Lockjaw Vest with the rest all rawhide.  I was wondering if anyone had any suggestions as to what the next logical armor upgrade is?  My vast wealth currently consists of 80PP from selling Greater Lightstones - which took a LOT of hunting - so I want to make sure I don't waste it on something stupid.<br>
<br>
Any suggestions are appreciated!<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
Tipkin <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utetriancorbec.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tetrian corbec</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/18/01 5:26:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor Upgrade</span><hr size=1> when you get to level 20 do the Testament of vanear quest, its pretty easy,<br>
you need to travel to Qeynos and talk to a guy there, and then you need to camp a guard in highhold pass (corupted one so no bad faction) and you have it. <br>
the highhold guy can be a looong camp (up to 8hours earth time)<br>
Reward is a 10wis 10mana book, that goes in off-hand.<br>
<br>
<br>
for other slots, you could buy a couple of wisdom rings, maybe earings (20pp?-3wis in each), black iron medalion(25pp-3wis also), split paw hide gloves(2wis-25pp),<br>
<br>
cant think of anything else right now.<br>
<br>
Good luck.<br>
<br>
Tet.<br>
